channel.title: Bad soundcloud uploads
channel.description:
Do you guys sometimes also scroll all the way down through your soundcloud page, listen to all your uploaded tracks, and repeatedly think: 'Wow this is so bad'. I have this for several of my uploaded tracks, and I'm seriously considering deleting them from my soundcloud page.
Is this familiar to some of you, or am I the only one? Curious..
